name: ObjectGraphIteratorTest
description: Unit tests for the ObjectGraphIterator class, which is used to iterate over a graph of objects.

nested_classes.name: Branch
nested_classes.description: Represents a branch in a tree structure with leaves.

nested_classes.name: Leaf
nested_classes.description: Represents a leaf in a tree structure with a color.

nested_classes.name: LeafFinder
nested_classes.description: Transformer that finds leaves in a forest structure.

nested_classes.name: Tree
nested_classes.description: Represents a tree structure with branches.

test_cases.name: testIteration_IteratorOfIterators
test_cases.description: Tests the iteration over a list of iterators using ObjectGraphIterator.

test_cases.name: testIteration_IteratorOfIteratorsWithEmptyIterators
test_cases.description: Tests the iteration over a list of iterators, including empty iterators, using ObjectGraphIterator.

test_cases.name: testIteration_RootNoTransformer
test_cases.description: Tests the iteration over a root object without a transformer using ObjectGraphIterator.

test_cases.name: testIteration_RootNull
test_cases.description: Tests the iteration over a null root object using ObjectGraphIterator.

test_cases.name: testIteration_Transformed1
test_cases.description: Tests the iteration over a transformed forest structure using ObjectGraphIterator.

test_cases.name: testIteration_Transformed2
test_cases.description: Tests the iteration over a transformed forest structure with multiple trees using ObjectGraphIterator.

test_cases.name: testIteration_Transformed3
test_cases.description: Tests the iteration over a transformed forest structure with multiple branches using ObjectGraphIterator.

test_cases.name: testIteratorConstructor_null_next
test_cases.description: Tests the behavior of ObjectGraphIterator when constructed with a null iterator and calling next().

test_cases.name: testIteratorConstructor_null_remove
test_cases.description: Tests the behavior of ObjectGraphIterator when constructed with a null iterator and calling remove().

test_cases.name: testIteratorConstructor_null1
test_cases.description: Tests the behavior of ObjectGraphIterator when constructed with a null iterator.

test_cases.name: testIteratorConstructorIteration_Empty
test_cases.description: Tests the iteration over an empty list of iterators using ObjectGraphIterator.

test_cases.name: testIteratorConstructorIteration_Simple
test_cases.description: Tests the iteration over a simple list of iterators using ObjectGraphIterator.

test_cases.name: testIteratorConstructorIteration_SimpleNoHasNext
test_cases.description: Tests the iteration over a simple list of iterators without using hasNext() using ObjectGraphIterator.

test_cases.name: testIteratorConstructorIteration_WithEmptyIterators
test_cases.description: Tests the iteration over a list of iterators, including empty iterators, using ObjectGraphIterator.

test_cases.name: testIteratorConstructorRemove
test_cases.description: Tests the remove operation during iteration over a list of iterators using ObjectGraphIterator.
